txt.en: Sensing the disparity of your enemy's situation, you take aim, and are able to bring about a swift end to the fight.
Kill Shot no longer has an inherent miss chance.\n
You have a [placeholder] chance to deal extra damage and reset the cooldown of Kill Shot when used on targets below 50% health.
You have a [placeholder] chance to deal extra damage and reset the cooldown of Kill Shot when used on targets below 25% health.
